              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Natural iron. For details see transmission data."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " Least squares fitting with an R-matrix representation",
                " of the cross section"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "  R-matrix. For narrow resonances the background",
                " taken from an interpolation from fits to adjacent",
                " wide resonances.",
                " Parameters of S-wave resonances up to 500keV were",
                " fits leaving out regions around smaller resonances.",
                " P-wave resonances, and finally resonances with width",
                " less than the resolution function were fitted.",
                " Some spins were deduced from fitted parameters.",
                " Adjustment of r(infinity) was included in S-wave",
                " region, but with a large covariance with the",
                " normalization.",
                " For linac data only three resonances were seen. The",
                " energy and neutron width of the first bound level in",
                " Fe-56 were deduced from data between 3eV and 3keV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Synchrocyclotron data",
                " background correction in energy range 70-300keV",
                " Re-normalization that decreased with increasing",
                "  neutron energy"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Uncertainty on the flight path and zero time gave",
                " an accuracy on energies of 1 in 10*4.",
                " The uncertainty on the neutron width due to",
                " covariance terms is between one and two times the",
                " statistical error."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Errors quoted are only statistical, one sigma."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Synchrocyclotron measurements on 2 mm and",
                " 60 mm samples will be included in final analysis."
              ]
            }
          ],
